channel.title: [Beta] RuneWave [Beta]
channel.description:
[CENTER]It's a great server but it's currently in beta, would love some help and suggestions. I'm currently using .webs but will change that in the future. [COLOR=red]As for now check it out at [URL=http://runewave.webs.com]runewave.webs.com[/URL][/COLOR]
Perfect PVP experience which is currently in development. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW1.png[/img]
Great PVM server, as that is what I enjoy most in a RSPS. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW2.png[/img]
Flawless summoning training. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW3.png[/img]
Flawless summoning training. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW4.png[/img]
Dungeoneering with many floors and complexities. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW5.png[/img]
Nex & Steel Titan. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW6.png[/img]
Items kept on death. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW7.png[/img]
Customizable completionist cape. [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW8.png[/img] [IMG]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/374/runewave.webs.com/RW9.png[/img][/CENTER]
